  "description": "<p>Employment Type: Full-Time</p>\n<p>Location: [Insert Restaurant Name / Location]</p>\n<p>Eligibility: Only Singapore Citizens / PR need apply</p>\n<p>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</p>\n<p>1. Prepare and cook menu items according to restaurant standards and recipes.</p>\n<p>2. Ensure food presentation and quality meet company expectations.</p>\n<p>3. Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of kitchen and cooking equipment.</p>\n<p>4. Assist in food preparation, portioning, and storage.</p>\n<p>5. Monitor food inventory and notify supervisor for replenishment.</p>\n<p>6. Comply with food safety and hygiene regulations at all times.</p>\n<p>7. Work with the team to ensure smooth kitchen operations.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<p>1. Singaporean / PR only.</p>\n<p>2. At least 1–2 years of cooking experience in a restaurant / café environment preferred.</p>\n<p>3. Knowledge of food hygiene and safety practices.</p>\n<p>4. Ability to work in a fast-paced environment.</p>\n<p>5. Team player with initiative and responsibility.</p>\n<p>6. Willing to work shifts, weekends, and public holidays.</p>",
